title: Emtek 4411 Marietta Tubular Entry Set in double finish
item_description:
Emtek 4411 Marietta Tubular Entry Set in double finish

  • Handing Required if Lever used on inside.
  • Available in Single Cylinder, Double Cylinder, or Full Dummy functions. Please specify when ordering.
  • Schlage C Keyway as standard.
  • Standard latch is for 2-3/8 in. backset. 2-3/4 in. available.
  • Note: 28 Degree Rotation Latch not available for for use with Tubular Entrance Handlesets.
  • Fits standard door thickness of 1-3/4 in. Specify if thicker.
  • Standard 2-1/8 in. door prep
